DESCRIPTION
Treat your little one to a nutritious blend of real peas and carrots for a delicious healthy snack with Full Cheeks Peas & Carrots Mix. Made with love for chinchillas, hamsters, and most small animals, this mix is made with real vegetables your small pet will love. We believe caring for your furry little one should be as easy as loving them, and now it can be. Our products are specially made for them, and are designed to be simple for you. All they need to do is what they do best: give lots of love. Only at PetSmart.
